50|$|<b>Smart</b> <b>antenna</b> {{research}} led to {{the development}} of 4G MIMO. Conventional <b>smart</b> <b>antenna</b> techniques (such as diversity and beamforming) deliver incremental gains in spectral efficiency. 4G MIMO exploits natural multipath propagation to multiply spectral efficiency.|$|E
